"2 cups dried lentils, rinsed and picked over","1  14-oz. can diced tomatoes","3  carrots, cut into 1/4-inch rounds","3  ribs celery, cut into 1/4-inch pieces","1  onion, finely chopped","2  cloves garlic, finely chopped","1/2 teaspoon dried oregano","5 cups low-sodium vegetable broth","  Salt and pepper","1 tablespoon red wine vinegar","1/4 cup chopped fresh parsley","  Grated Parmesan, optional"